Manchester City have increased season tickets from £870 to £1,700 for able-bodied fans . 
  Some disabled fans say they are 'disgusted' with the club after they hiked prices by 283 per cent . 
  The club are accused of trying to relocate disabled fans to other parts of the Etihad Stadium . 
  The disabled bays are in the same section of the stadium as the regular season tickets . 
 